  Locus:
    Page: 326
    Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Moderation
---
If a man oversteps the limits of moderation, he pollutes his body and mind.
To be god-like is to be natural; to be natural is to follow Nature...(i.e.,
to keep) within the limits set by instinct and reason.
